####Architecture#####
Namespace: internal
   ↓
Deployment (nginx)
   ↓
ClusterIP Service
   ↓
Ingress (gce)
   ↓
Google HTTPS Load Balancer (auto-created)
   ↓↓↓↓ 
Deployed Network Policy:
Default deny all
Allow DNS
Allow specific external IP only



kubectl apply -f namespace.yml
kubectl apply -f deployment.yml
kubectl apply -f denyall.yml
kubectl apply -f allow-specific-egress.yml
kubectl apply -f ingress.yml
kubectl get ingress -n internal

Test:
curl -k -H "Host: app.example.com" https://34.149.113.83
